rComments: only one assignment worth 50% and final worth 50%. he reads off the powerpoints then shares the powerpoints so his class is really boring. Final is very hard and all multiple choice since he concentrates on the most minor details of Canadian history. he is not specific about what he is looking for on the big assignment

I had this professor for a french immersion history class and he was an excellent choice. Easy to understand and he's funny and helpful if you ever have questions. The class only had a paper and a final which made each very stressful but it lightened the course load for the rest of the semester. Lots of reading & each slide show was like 90 slides.
teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Get ready to read']
